{"tid":2080450,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"31 想點 (推到完場)","createTime":"2020-06-26T12:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T01:48:56.000Z","uid":54517,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"331272d8132d28b8a684c5ed75695149acbe7c5f","tid":2080450,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"監製：張詠賢<br />\n<br />\n26/06/2020<br />\n免於恐懼的自由是現代文明社會的基本人權。<br />\n在香港，哪些事物會令我們恐懼？<br />\n面對相同的事物，有人覺得恐懼，有人覺得安心。<br />\n社會和制度變化，是令恐懼愈來愈少抑或愈多愈多？恐懼是問題，還是答案？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘉賓：梁芷珊（香港企業家／填詞人／作家）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主持／編導：麥嘉緯"},{"pid":"798dd4a73b1ba9e65def77d30306321295a68ba0","tid":2080450,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c10589b600c2b510381b53d0e76d3a00f0e926","tid":2080450,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e30805e42f796ea7b2a79aa465c0ad569001e0c","tid":2080450,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /